<L>__{interior mozart's workroom day 1780's}
<A>__{mozart stands trying to blot out the noise of his father's shouting from the next room.}
<C>__{leopold }
<D>__{dinner at eight! dinner at ten! dinner when anyone feels like it! if anyone feels like it!}
<A>__{the ensemble of ah, tutti contenti! saremo cosi from act iv of figaro resumes, coming to his aid and rising to greet the listener with its serene harmonies. relieved, mozart languidly picks up his cue and plays a shot on the billiard table: he is sucked back into his own world of sound.}
